node.text: @calmbo and I been hitting Evergreen park for sunset sesh the last could days🛹🛹🌄 fun trying out this new #goprohero7black camera 🎥 🤘🏻🛹🎥 #skatekilning

“Seguso Remibulator” Collaboration with my man @mikeramanglass 🖤🤍🖤🤍🖤🤍
We made this one for our drop @greenplanetsmokeshop last night #sold to a private collector. 🖤🤍 this is the first angled neck Remib! Thanks for looking! Hope everyone had a great 7/10 holiday!💨💨💨💨🖤🤍

node.text:
“Backside Flip” I’m having my third annual skate contest this Saturday 6/19/21 @curbsideskatepark with @exploreglassgallery 🛹🌊🛹 there will be a best backside flip contest and the winner will win a one of a kind piece of glass I personally made. We will have prizes for 1-3rd places🎉🎉🎉 I will have some new work on display and collaborations with @shengoines @mikelunaglass @darbyholmglass and @pipemaker 🛹🎉🛹🎉❤️
 Special Guest appearances from @clintwalker @devinbagnoli @jworthit 🛹🙏🏻 

A huge thank you to @303boards for their donation and support! 🛹⚡️💯

  If your interested in skating in the contest please DM @exploreglassgallery 🛹🤟🏻🎉

node.text:
Elisabeth Goines 2/7/1956 - 5/19/2021 

To those of you that knew or met my mom @libbygoines I’m sure you know how special she was. I wouldn’t be the artist I am today without her. She loved our community and she loved all of you that supported her and her art. We are all missing her very much. I really appreciate all of you that reached out in messages and commented on my last post. Thank you. 
  We are planning a memorial for Libby on June 6th at 1pm in Takilma Oregon. If you feel that you want to come to honor Libby’s life please reach out to me in messages or text me if you have my number. Sending love to all. ❤️
